#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:2
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Descripción general"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :mod:`~qilisdk.functionals` module provides high-level quantum "
"execution procedures by combining tools from the :mod:`~qilisdk.analog`, "
":mod:`~qilisdk.digital`, and :mod:`~qilisdk.core` modules. Currently, it "
"includes the following execution functionals:"
msgstr ""
"El módulo :mod:`~qilisdk.functionals` proporciona procedimientos de "
"ejecución cuántica de alto nivel combinando herramientas de los módulos "
":mod:`~qilisdk.analog`, :mod:`~qilisdk.digital` y :mod:`~qilisdk.core`. "
"Actualmente incluye los siguientes functionals de ejecución:"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:7
msgid ""
":doc:`functionals_digital`: Propagates a digital quantum circuit through "
"the backend."
msgstr ""
":doc:`functionals_digital`: Propaga un circuito cuántico digital a través"
" del backend."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:8
msgid ""
":doc:`functionals_analog`: Simulates analog time evolution of one or more"
" Hamiltonians according to a time-dependent schedule."
msgstr ""
":doc:`functionals_analog`: Simula la evolución temporal analog de uno o "
"más Hamiltonianos según un schedule dependiente del tiempo."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:9
msgid ""
":doc:`functionals_reservoirs`: Runs a quantum reservoir pipeline (pre-"
"processing, reservoir dynamics, post-processing) across multiple input "
"layers."
msgstr ""
":doc:`functionals_reservoirs`: Ejecuta un pipeline de quantum reservoir "
"(preprocesamiento, dinámica del reservoir, postprocesamiento) a través de"
" múltiples capas de entrada."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:11
msgid ""
"Moreover, it provides more complex functionals that are used to execute "
"more complex algorithms:"
msgstr ""
"Además, proporciona functionals más complejos que se utilizan para "
"ejecutar algoritmos más complejos:"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:13
msgid ""
":doc:`functionals_variational`: Builds a parameterized program to be "
"optimized in a hybrid quantum-classical environment."
msgstr ""
":doc:`functionals_variational`: Construye un programa parametrizado para "
"ser optimizado en un entorno híbrido cuántico-clásico."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:16
msgid "Architecture Overview"
msgstr "Descripción general de la arquitectura"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:18
msgid ""
"Every functional conforms to the abstract "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.Functional` interface. Primitive "
"functionals such as "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation` and "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution` also "
"inherit from "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.PrimitiveFunctional`, which mixes"
" in the :class:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable` contract. "
"This lets backends query and update symbolic parameters consistently "
"before execution."
msgstr ""
"Cada functional se ajusta a la interfaz abstracta "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.Functional`. Los functionals "
"primitivos como "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation` y "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution` también "
"heredan de :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.PrimitiveFunctional`, "
"que incorpora el contrato "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable`. Esto permite que "
"los backends consulten y actualicen parámetros simbólicos de forma "
"coherente antes de la ejecución."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:25
msgid ""
"Readout is decoupled from functionals: measurement details (shots, "
"observables, state tomography) are specified via :mod:`~qilisdk.readout` "
"objects passed to the backend's "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute` method. All primitive "
"functionals return a unified "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`."
msgstr ""
"La lectura está desacoplada de los functionals: los detalles de medición "
"(shots, observables, tomografía de estado) se especifican mediante "
"objetos :mod:`~qilisdk.readout` que se pasan al método "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute` del backend. Todos los "
"functionals primitivos devuelven un "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` "
"unificado."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:30
msgid "Result Objects"
msgstr "Objetos de resultado"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:32
msgid ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`"
msgstr ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:33
msgid ""
"The unified result type for all primitive functionals. Access results "
"through: ``samples`` for shot counts, ``probabilities`` for measurement "
"probabilities, ``state`` for the terminal "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` state (when using "
":meth:`~qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_state_tomography`), and"
" ``expectation_values`` for expectation values (when using "
":meth:`~qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_expectation`). When "
"``store_intermediate_results=True``, intermediate results are available "
"via ``intermediate_states``, ``intermediate_samples``, "
"``intermediate_probabilities``, and ``intermediate_expectation_values``."
msgstr ""
"El tipo de resultado unificado para todos los functionals primitivos. Se "
"accede a los resultados mediante: ``samples`` para los conteos de shots, "
"``probabilities`` para las probabilidades de medición, ``state`` para el "
"estado terminal :class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` (al usar "
":meth:`~qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_state_tomography`), y "
"``expectation_values`` para los valores esperados (al usar "
":meth:`~qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_expectation`). Cuando "
"``store_intermediate_results=True``, los resultados intermedios están "
"disponibles mediante ``intermediate_states``, ``intermediate_samples``, "
"``intermediate_probabilities`` e ``intermediate_expectation_values``."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:40
msgid ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program_result.VariationalProgramResult`"
msgstr ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program_result.VariationalProgramResult`"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_overview.rst:41
msgid ""
"bundles the optimizer trajectory (optimal cost, parameters, intermediate "
"steps) together with the functional result obtained at convergence."
msgstr ""
"agrupa la trayectoria del optimizador (costo óptimo, parámetros, pasos "
"intermedios) junto con el resultado funcional obtenido en la "
"convergencia."

